{"tid":1098042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家香港女仔好多都係雞。","createTime":"2019-04-08T19:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T03:31:50.000Z","uid":237675,"like":19,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a9e900421329fe3a677ea16a084fbd67d4ca8de1","tid":1098042,"uid":237675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T19:25:08.000Z","msg":"就算而家唔係都唔代表以前唔係。<br />\n更何況將來。<br />\n 個個女仔為咗1000幾百。<br />\n就出賣自己。影裸照/做雞。<br />\n其實都幾可悲。<br />\n有時見有啲女仔斯斯文文好似好保守。<br />\n到最後咪又係俾人搵返以前嘅裸照. <br />\n一係就死口唔認，一係就話咩細個唔識諗。<br />\n你估個個係天真嬌咩，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前唔同意各位ching 成日話個個女仔都係雞 係公廁 乜9嘢三百就屌得。<br />\n而家發覺大家講得冇錯。香港真係好多雞。<br />\n<br />\n好彩我唔係雞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1455fb364a8f0db715fe92843676850477c4da33","tid":1098042,"uid":11598,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T19:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兜咁大個圈就係想講自己唔係"},{"pid":"4e1e7658e29aac95b7880a6109548ebd5b33829a","tid":1098042,"uid":237675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T19:30:58.000Z","msg":"負評我嘅 應該係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44da8e2d3196f454fee80190c5e1ef916c7b7277","tid":1098042,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1455fb364a8f0db715fe92843676850477c4da33","tid":1098042,"uid":11598,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T19:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兜咁大個圈就係想講自己唔係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T19:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fa25e8386b55116d646441b18db89b6d3df3b6","tid":1098042,"uid":